name: Talif's Journey
description: Join Talif in his journey as he travels to 4 dungeons on his path from Apprentice to Wizard. Call upon earth, fire, water, and air as you master all 4 elements! Combine the elemental orbs to create spells that are greater than the sum of their parts.

name: Karar X
description: Karar X is a puzzle-adventure game with a decision-based story-end. It requires you to use 4 special characters with different skills to solve the unique puzzles.

name: Horace: First Trip
description: Before the first wedding night, the main character’s bride was abducted. The long-awaited chance to become a man was lost too. The game’s goal — saving the princess. The player controls the main character by WASD keys. The genre — an arcade. Language — Russian/English.

name: Aquanaut no Kyuujitsu: Memories of Summer 1996
Future Noir
description: Future Noir is an adventure game that combines elements of first-person shooters and walking simulators. You must solve a crime that will take you to remote places in a dystopian future and lead you to discover things that perhaps you were better off without knowing. Are you ready?

name: TwilightStar: Heart of Eir
description:
In TS:Heart of Eir, you will experience a world governing a delicate balance. With the people of Eathral learning to navigate the growing developments around Stryah usage (our magic system, more on that later!) in significant times of turbulence and upheaval, you will carry our protagonist Eir (and her companions) on a journey to discover just what it means to sustain peace, and confront the destinies and darkness we're not always prepared for.

Eathral is crumbling.

The Stryah crystals that shine like starlight, imbuing the planet's surface with mystical and powerful magicks are turning black, and pockets of chaos are sprouting all across the continent. But in the reclusive village of Homaran, a tentative peace is sustained amongst its people.

Eir lives simply with her father; her life plain but fulfilling. Until he is brutally murdered at the hands of the Caelki, a dark sect who live in service to disorder and the worship of an insatiable god, long since forgotten to legend, much like the origins of the crystals Eathral has come to so desperately rely on.

With her closest companion and unrequited inamorata, Kira at her heel and a mysterious book written in a language she does not understand, Eir sets out on a quest to find answers that will reshape her destiny and change everything she knows about who she thought she was. Taking refuge in the hands of her allies and a planetary ancestral power that roots itself deeper within her than even she knows, Eir must learn to wield the might of Eathral herself in this tale of magical discovery, devotion, betrayal, and adventure.

name: My Brother the Sacrifice
description: A short, top-down game where you'll try to save your brother from the Goddess of Death and her cult of followers.

name: Whirled
description:
Whirled is a virtual world website and video game created by Three Rings Design. Its Open Beta stage was announced at the Game Developers Conference in 2007. It makes use of Adobe Flash as an applet embedded into the website while also having pages of HTML and JavaScript in a sidebar to allow players to manage their friends list and browse various categories of user-generated content.

The concept is comparable to the virtual worlds in the PlayStation 3 game Home and Second Life, while also incorporating aspects of feed-based social media sites like Facebook and Twitter. It pushes to make all content user-created, mainly with its approach to creative accessibility using Flash's affinity for 2D vector graphics and various web compatibilities to make it very simple for players to upload a wide variety of content using simple, conventional file formats.

Upon Grey Havens releasing the source code for Whirled under their BSD License, several mirror sites formed. While they had no access to the original database, a lot of content was copied across to create a similar experience managed by the community.

The Whirled Club is the only mirror sites that is active at the moment. You can download the client here to load flash content [ https://wcmedia.xyz/client/wcclient-v1.1.2-setup.exe ].

Source: Wikipedia

name: Leapoid
description: Leap, fall, and perish — over and over again. Only the most seasoned platforming veterans will overcome the trials that leapoid has to offer.

name: Space Viking Raiders VR
description: Looking for an online co-op game to play through with friends? You want a hilarious story with full voice acting! Diablo meets Gauntlet in this dungeon crawler action RPG. Wreck havoc with physics and mass destruction in SPACE VIKING RAIDERS! Wishlist now!

name: Whispers From the Rift
description: An original action, sci-fi, interactive novel with a unique 4th wall harnessing twist. ​Enter the mind of a black-ops team leader heading up an impossible mission in the year 2028. Experience events as they happen in first-person and whisper commands that must be obeyed.

name: Final Fantasy Brave Exvius Chocobo Run!
You Complete Me
description: Dexterity, tenacity and brainpower. You'll need all of these and more to succeed in this completionist quest to awaken an ancient island. The world is becoming overpopulated. As you venture across oceans in search of new land you pick up a strange radio signal. Is it a voice? Is it asking for help?

Treasure Gaust: Gaust Diver - Deep Purple

Having secured a contract to collect some money from a town on the other shore, everything should be plain sailing ahead for the duo, but of course, the best laid plans of mice and wolves often go awry…

name: Riku to Johan: Kaeta Nimai no E
Reporter 2
description:
The continuation of the popular action-horror game - "Reporter" from "AGaming+" studio, will shock you to the core! Turn off the lights, connect headphones and be careful, because only the attentive and cautious person can finally unravel this dark history!
You somehow miraculously survived in the hospital! Do you think it is over? And what about that strange call about 7 days? The time is running out! Carefree dreams are left behind: now you are hostage of nightmares and wake up in a cold sweat every morning. And nightmares are becoming more realistic and eerie every day. That's why you are trying to find out something about that mysterious girl, who is following you in nightmares. One of your friends found out something interesting and you need to start your action, immediately! It's time to go!

name: Outscape
description: Outscape is a 4X Space Strategy MMO set in a huge Persistent Online Galaxy. Experience strategic gameplay in a universe with thousands of other players. Build an empire, colonize, research, design ships, ally, trade and fight to ensure your civilization’s survival.

Paul Sloane & Des MacHale's Intriguing Tales
Oshare Princess DS: Oshare ni Koi Shite 2
My Stop Smoking Coach: Allen Carr's EasyWay
Enzbots
description: Split screen, co-op, easy to play, but hard to master. 13 levels, pool, soccer, mini golf while defending your life.4 unique characters, verse an army of enemies, all my own design.Hours of re-playable fun, for any age or skill level, kid friendly, girlfriend friendly, designed to put players in a good mood.

Kidou Senshi Gundam: Gundam vs. Z Gundam
Katekyo Hitman Reborn! DS Flame Rumble X

Explore vast planets, stars and encounter new challenges that lie around every corner. With unique themes and missions, MechZ9 allows you to uncover the true mystery of the Mechaverse. Our game is designed with the player in mind, giving you the freedom to explore, immerse yourself in the game and experience the thrill of space exploration like never before.

name: Euroscope
description: One of the available ATC Software to connect to the VATSIM network as a controller.

name: Nugget Royale

It probably found the same fate as other Hi Tech games like Bobby's world, in which the market was too saturated for platformers based on cartoons.

name: The Puppet of Tersa: A Curious Place
FlickaDrink
description:
You've acquired an abandoned saloon, and its time to get the old shack cleaned up, furnished and full of customers!
Serve your short tempered patrons, before they get all fighty. Spend your earnings to improve your service and on decorating the saloon.

Get the tables full of guests, and be sure to flick those drinks to the right customer.

- Match drink colors to the customers orders, before they leave or start fighting.
- Knock out the angriest patrons.
- Manage the bar, when it gets rowdier every night!

Acquire wealth and expand your enterprise beyond the saloon and play sevaral wild west themed minigames.

description: It's time to get into the mini swing of things with Crazy Mini Golf 2! Choose from 4 differently themed worlds and 18 fun and challenging holes in each world.

description: Defend your limited food supply from hoards of super-powered ants!

name: Aye Captain!
description: In Aye Captain! as a Pirate Captain you recruit and manage crew members, acquire new ships and upgrade them to cross swords and cannons with many other swashbucklers during turn based battles.

name: ClayFighter: Call of Putty
description: ClayFighter: Call of Putty was an unreleased game for the Nintendo DSi and Wii. The game was going to be a remake of ClayFighter: Sculptor's Cut, with the same characters and stages, although much of the stages got redesigns. It was supposed to include a story mode, a training mode, and multiplayer mode where up to two players can fight, and Claytalities. The game's was planned to release in 2011 for DsiWare and WiiWare.

name: Widow's Woods - A Southfog Mini Adventure
Lumiette
description: Dodge magical bullets in an imaginary sonicscape.

name: Konji
description: Konji is a top-down PC game consisting of plenty of items and enemies, and progressively more difficult bosses throughout the game. The player can collect weapons, specials, helmets, rings and pets from loot dropped by enemies to upgrade their character and fight tougher enemies.

Muscle Ranking Vol.1: Ore ga Saikyou no Otoko da!
LoveSick Darlings

Cowboy Valley
description: Outlaws stole you precious pet Daisy and blew up the ranch. Chase the bandits through spectacular biomes, bring them to justice and retrieve the precious piggy! Restore the ranch and fill it with all sorts of cattle you catch along the way!

name: The Deep Deep
description: The Deep Deep is a tactical dungeon crawler in a side-scrolling environment. Explore dark mines, ruined cities, and lava-filled caverns; solve puzzles and battle enemies to unlock dwarven classes and find treasure.

name: The Video Game Machine
description: The ultimate video game sandbox! Create, explore, and survive across a retro gaming universe. Gather heroes, forge weapons, and build worlds - the adventures are endless!

name: Skyweaver
description: Skyweaver is a free-to-play competitive trading card game from another dimension. Customize your decks to suit any playstyle, gain the allegiance of ethereal creatures in Sky, and ascend the ranks to become a legendary Skyweaver!

name: Hottarake no Shima: Kanata to Nijiiro no Kagami
Past Fate
description: Past Fate is an open world MMORPG set in medieval fantasy world where the players freedom is the key element. Choose what you will become and explore the vast world and its continents for hidden secrets and mysteries. What is your fate?

name: Hermina to Culus: Lillie no Atelier Mou Hitotsu no Monogatari
Daisenryaku Daitoua Kouboushi DX: Dai-ni-ji Sekai Taisen
Last Week
description: Napa, a girl who has been haunted by a nightmare since childhood, decided to take a step into the abandoned school she saw in the dream. Something attempted to drag her into the past and it will never let her go back.

name: One Punch Man: The Strongest Man
Dragon Side II: The Twisted Speare
Sketchful.io
description:
Sketchful.io is a massively multiplayer free to play pictionary IO game! 
 
The goal of pictionary is simple! 
Every round, one person gets to choose a word and draw it to their best ability. 
The rest of the players have to guess what they think the word is as fast as they can. 
The person with the most points at the end of the game is the winner!

name: War of Ashird
description:
War of Ashird is a unique game that combines all the elements of SRPG and the elements of managing your castle. The story focus on a young boy who, by a twist of fate, becomes a key player in the war between three powerful nations: the Prisean Empire, the Kingdom of Ceredia, and the Free Cities' Alliance. From his humble beginnings, our hero will rise in rank through his mighty deeds on the battlefield-until he commands an army of his own.
Your choices will shape his destiny, and the future of the Ashird as well...

name: Dear Toki
description: Write letters to reconnect with a friend

name: Kodawari Saihai Simulation: Ocha no Ma Pro Yakyuu DS
Tarkus and the Crystal of Fear
Lume and the Shifting Void
description: Join Lume in a fight against the other-dimensional hordes of The Shifting Void with her experimental Holostrikers in this platform-action adventure!

name: Who Killed My Sister?
description: I came home from a family trip only to find my sister dead. She has left me mysterious messages as her dying wish.

name: Omni Axes
description: Trust your instincts - evade, aim, and shoot! Omni Axes is a shooting game that takes place in a 3D space where you can take down an endless number of enemies coming from all directions.

name: Digging Day
description: A Cute and Simple Farming, Selling and Crafting Game.

name: Plastic Love
description: In Plastic Love you will play as owner of house of pleasures. Design, build and repair robot like dolls, which will satisfy your clients' most secret fantasies. Make your plastic empire the most desirable!

name: The Heart Pumps Clay
description: In The Heart Pumps Clay, players take control over Mara, a swamp witch, her golem, Bud, and the aptly named Crow as they climb the Tree of Life in order to obtain the Source of All Things.

name: Fukakutei Sekai no Tantei Shinshi Virginal Vol. 2
Fukakutei Sekai no Tantei Shinshi Virginal Vol. 1
Bakumatsu Renka: Shinsengumi DS
description: A port of Bakumatsu Renka: Shinsengumi for the Nintendo DS.

name: The Klaxo Radio Hour
description: A perfectly safe radio that is not haunted. Offering a rare chance to be a part of Radio History!

name: Fibber Kit
description: Fibber Kit - a sandbox for the inventor. Create your own mechanism or experiment!

name: Colonies End
description: Colonies End is a sci-fi, adventure, sandbox game set among the stars. You’ll be mining, constructing, advancing and discovering to survive in these dimension spanning realms.

name: Alchemist Dungeon
description: The young alchemist girl Annelle, on the orders of the Dark Amethyst guild, sets off in search of a philosopher's stone, which can turn any metal into gold. The abandoned alchemists' dungeon, located near the Gelbin city, where rumors are about the numerous riches stored inside, indicated its location.

name: NetPanzer
description: NetPanzer is an online multiplayer tactical warfare game designed for fast action combat. Gameplay concentrates on the core - no resource management is needed. The game is based on quick tactical action and unit management in real-time. Battles progress quickly and constantly as destroyed players respawn with a set of new units. Players can join or leave games at any time.

name: Nortinium
description: Help Arthur Shadowstrike on his quest to find the eight "Rings of Destiny" on this challenging puzzle platformer. £1 of every sale will go to charity.

name: Evol Online
description: Evol Online is a 2D fantasy-style game which aims to create a friendly environment for interacting with others where people can escape reality and enjoy themselves.

name: Gnome Aisleriot
description:
Aisleriot — also known as sol or solitaire — is a card game
application that features over 80 different solitaire-type card
games which are designed to play using a mouse, keyboard, or trackpad.

name: Gnome Taquin
description: Taquin is a computer version of the 15-puzzle and other sliding puzzles. The object of Taquin is to move tiles so that they reach their places, either indicated with numbers, or with parts of a great image.

name: Gnome Hitori
description: Hitori is a small application written to allow one to play the eponymous puzzle game, which is similar in theme to more popular puzzles such as Sudoku.

name: Gnome Tali
description: Tali is a sort of poker with dice and less money. You roll five dice three times and try to create the best hand. Your two rerolls may include any or all of your dice. Tali also supports playing Kismet.

name: Gnome Robots
description: The classic robots game where you have to avoid a hoard of robots who are trying to kill you. Each step you take brings them closer toward you. Fortunately they aren't very smart and you also have a helpful teleportation gadget.

name: Gnome Nibbles
description: The aim of the game is to swallow as many objects as you can while avoiding maze walls and other worms.

name: Gnome Four in a Row
description: The objective of Four-in-a-row is to build a line of four of your marbles while trying to stop your opponent (human or computer) building a line of his or her own. A line can be horizontal, vertical or diagonal.

name: Gnome Swell Foop
description: The goal is to remove the objects in as few moves as possible. Similar objects that are adjacent to each other are removed as a group. The remaining objects then collapse to fill in the gaps and new groups are formed. You cannot remove single objects.

name: Gnome Lights Off
description: Lights Off is a puzzle game, where the objective is to turn off all of the tiles on the board. Each click toggles the state of the clicked tile and its non-diagonal neighbors.

name: Gnome Iagno
description: Iagno is a computer version of the game Reversi, more popularly called Othello. Iagno is a two player strategy game similar to Go. The board is 8 by 8 with tiles that are black on one side and white on the other side. The object of Iagno is to flip as many of your opponent's tiles to your color as possible without your opponent flipping your tiles. This is done by trapping your opponent's tiles between two tiles of your own color.

name: Gnome Tetravex
description: Tetravex is a simple puzzle where pieces must be positioned so that the same numbers are touching each other. Your game is timed, these times are stored in a system-wide scoreboard.

name: Gnome Sudoku
description:
Sudoku is a Japanese logic game that exploded in popularity in 2005.

Gnome Sudoku was originally programmed in Python by Thomas Hinkle, though it has since been rewritten. It is meant to have an interface as simple and unobstrusive as possible while still providing features that make playing difficult Sudoku more fun.

name: Gnome Mahjongg
description: Mahjongg is a solitaire (one player) version of the classic Eastern tile game, Mahjongg. The objective is to select pairs of similar tiles.

name: Gnome Five or More
description: Remove colored balls from the board by forming lines

name: BattleSky Brigade: Tribes
description:
BattleSky Brigade is a real-time strategy game which blends defend and raid elements with the drama of interdependent connected territories. You’ll play as a band of explorers setting up camp on a Wylde – a desolate mesa suspended in the air, high above the obliterated remains of the world below. 
 
Raid other Wyldes for resources and grow in power, all while forging alliances in the form of warbands, with everyone pitching in to aid your brethren to defend their territories from enemy raids.

name: Gnome Klotski
description: This game is a clone of the Klotski game. The objective is to move the patterned block to the area bordered by green markers.

name: Gnome Mines
description: A puzzle game where you locate mines floating in an ocean using only your brain and a little bit of luck.

name: Gnome Chess
description: Gnome Chess is a graphical front-end featuring a 2D and a 3D chessboard interface. Gnome Chess does not comprise an own chess engine and to play against the computer a third party chess engine must be present, but most Linux distributions package Gnu Chess as the default chess engine with it. Additionally Gnome Chess supports third party chess engines, known ones are automatically detected.

name: Actua Pool
description: Actua Pool lets players hustle their way around the local pool circuit to unlock different clubs and challengers in an effort to win cash and prove who is King of the Cue. The DS touch screen and Stylus provides the perfect interface for pool allowing gamers to dictate everything through touch. They use the stylus to line up shots, set the power, determine the cue angle and add spin to the ball.

name: A Rat's Quest: The Way Back Home
description: Follow Mat, the Scavenger, on his long journey to find his way back home. Experience a world full of threats from a rat's unique perspective, while fighting and sneaking on a rodent's most dangerous adventure.

name: Mining Rail 2
description:
Mining Rail 2 is a roller coaster game. 
 
Get into your mine cart and drive at high speed along the railway track, getting through the mine to the exit and down to the valley. The track is steep, the curves tight and the force tries to take your vehicle out of the bend. A good pilot now shifts the weight, tilts the mine cart in the curve and manages every tricky part of the track.

name: Angry Birds POP 2
description: When mysterious portals opened, spewing bubbles from the sky, these former rivals wasted no time formulating an action plan. That plan – pop the bubbles!

name: Inmortis
description:
Back from the dead after being sacrificed during a bloody ritual to bring old and forgotten deities into your reality, Inmortis invites you to discover a mystical world that changes depending on your actions.

Throughout your journey, you will face difficult choices that will make you question your morality along with challenging battles in which each mistake can lead to a horrible death...

name: Code: Realize ~Guardian of Rebirth~ Collector's Edition
Sky Beneath
description: This narratively driven puzzle platformer puts you in the role of Cassie, an intrepid scavenger seeking salvage in abandoned mining facilities. Embark on an adventure with your inventor friend Annie, take control of the gravity, and solve challenging puzzles in a mysterious sci-fi setting.

name: V Prototype
description: A top down shmup with a unique pulse attack and associated combo system.

name: Roy Cluse: Itsy-Bitsy Edition
description: The itsy-bitsy spider was bullied by rogue A.I., forced to run through angry plants, and try not to die!

name: Playing Both Sides
description: Playing Both Sides is a JRPG with a unique battle system and 10+ hours of play.

name: Two Kingdoms
description: In the game TWO KINGDOMS you have to defend your castle from an evil neighbor.

name: Moose Antipoo Adventure
description: MOOSE antipoo adventure - top-down action game about the Knight Elk and dirty mutants.

name: Pelmesh
description: Pelmesh is a fun physical arcade game about Pelmeshka, which is trying to get out of the Cat.

name: Old School Maze
description: Get out of the maze of nostalgia.

name: Nocturne: Rebirth
description: Nocturne: Rebirth is a popular 10 to 20-hour (story-wise) JRPG originally created using RPG Maker XP in 2009 by Shou (or Cogwheel). It is actually the remake of the game Nocturne created using RPG Maker 2000 way back in 2002. The differences between the two include new graphics and a new battle system, with only the story virtually unchanged. It was fan translated by eplipswich.

name: Dice Hunter: Quest of the Dicemancer
description:
Dice Hunter is a unique turn-based RPG with collectible dice. Master its clever combination of skill and luck. Enjoy tactical battles now!
Become a Dicemancer and assume the incredible ability to capture creatures into dice. Hunt dice and wield them to save the Land of Chance from the marauding minions and evil allies of the wicked Snake Eyes.

name: Zac to Ombra: Maboroshi no Yuuenchi
Zhu Zhu Pets: Quest for Zhu
Divinum
description: A mysterious island - home to the remains of an ancient civilization. An expedition turned into sacrifices for a horrific ritual. A young girl left as the only assumed survivor. Help her attain the power of the Ancient Gods in Divinum - and decide the fate of the world!

name: Cthulhu: Books of Ancients
description: Cthulhu: Books of Ancients is a first-person horror game in which we take on the role of a detective looking for a missing six children. A mysterious note thrown by an unknown informant at the door led him to the library of the University of Miskatonic, where there are clues to solve the puzzle.

name: Escoteiros Espaciais
description: Escoteiros Espaciais is a "connect-the-collumns" vocabulary game about Brazillian Sign Language (Libras) and Brazillian Portuguese! Currently avaiable in Brazillian Portuguese and Brazillian Sign Language Libras only.

name: Mondo Museum
description: Mondo Museum is a management sim that challenges you to construct, administer, and curate your own museum. Choose what items to showcase, draw in the crowds, and grow your collection of cultural, artistic, historical, and scientific displays to expand from a humble exhibit hall into a world-class institution!

name: Devilish: Ball Bounder
description: A breakout clone video game developed by Starfish for the Nintendo DS. It is the third entry in the Devilish series, released 13 years after Devilish: The Next Possession for the Genesis and like its predecessor, it is a game in the same genre of Breakout and Arkanoid, with elaborate fantasy visuals.

name: Poupée Girl DS 2: Sweet Pink Style
Reader Rabbit: on a Mission to Help the Lion Flowers
Monster planet
description: This is a third person action game,Players are located on a planet full of monsters,Players are free to explore the surrounding area,Players must survive as long as possible, either by killing or avoiding monsters,Monster leaders are dangerous to watch out for.

name: Stellar Swing
description: Stellar Swing is a fast-paced physics action game that'll have you swinging around open-ended levels to locate rare green energy crystals and collectibles.

name: Story: The Afterlife Heaven of Hell
Light Trail Rush
description: Light Trail Rush is an arcade-style hybrid of vehicular brawler and free-flow 3D space flight.

name: Run Kitty Run
description: Run Kitty Run is a chaotic online co-op game with teams up to six players. You and your fellow kittens must work together to get through maps filled with dangers. Use wisely your set of skills and purchasable items to aid you in this adventure.

name: Idiot Test
description: Idiot Test - a comic test for an idiot. Funny questions on ingenuity and quick wits!

name: Knife road
description: Take you through different time and space, Experience different customs of time and space, Meeting the challenges posed by time and space.

name: Marshmallow Madness
description: Defeat waves of opposing Marshmallows by pushing, burning or blowing them up! Will you survive the relentless onslaught of evil Marshmallows or will they overwhelm you in this chaotic brawler?

name: Lumbermill
description: Build, manage and maintain a Lumber Mill deep in the forest!

name: Broken Spell
description: Broken Spell is an ARPG game. You will fight side by side with your Master to cruel and ferocious demons and sorcerers.

name: Home A Drone
description: My Pa said the world would go to hell once Artificially Intelligent drones took over. I don’t much care what they do, as long as they stay off my damn lawn and out of my business!

name: Sente
description: Sente is an abstract strategy board game, with electricity, shields, lasers, and explosions, for 2 to 6 players that move simultaneously, where each move can cause a cascade of consequences while the board seeks to regain balance.

name: Dithered
description: Explore the mysterious and almost dreamlike world of Dithered. Heat, feed, and defend yourself. And if that doesn’t work, put your food in bonfires. You'll probably die, your food may spoil, and your shack will almost certainly burn to the ground.

name: It Pays to Be a Winner
description: Simple on the surface, but complex deep below, It Pays To Be A Winner is a 1v1 turn-based strategy game that pits players brain against brain across a square-tile landscape. It's kind of like chess, but not at all.

name: Naima's Melody
description:
Naima's Melody is a 2d zelda-like action adventure game! 
 
A Pre-Alpha/Tech Demo is available on the itch.io page to illustrate a foundation for the game but the next version of the game will be drastically different. 
 
The Demo will give players the chance to experience the core gameplay mechanics such as horse-back riding, exploring, combat, and puzzle-solving.

name: Capsize
description: Capsize is a rogue-like, deck-building, single player adventure. Build your pirate crew, stealing crew members from the other factions and promote them to unlock new powers. All in comic hand-drawn 2D style.

name: Penguins vs. Bugs
description: When a penguin entomologist's specimens are set loose, a team of penguins works to recover the escaped bugs as quickly as possible. Our penguin hero sets out to immobilize the insects so that the rest of the team can capture them.

name: Winter Cometh
description: Choose your faction and battle against other players with massive armies and AI camps or raids. In a dynamic environment from growing kingdoms and changing weather effecting far more than just the worlds appearance. To obtain the power and become the one true king. Beware Winter Cometh.

name: Herogrinder: Tactical Combat Arenas
description: The most ruthless game show of the 24th century where contestants enter lethal tactical combat arenas with customized bioroid soldiers and measure their skills against each other in simultaneous turn-based PvP and co-op deathmatches. A game of strategic combat with a sinister agenda.

name: General Coco
description: All eggs from the chicken coop were stolen. It's time to punish all the abductors who encroached on someone else's good!

name: Cult of the Abyss
description: Cult of the Abyss is a cute-horror-survival-sandbox. You and your Dog against the world. A whimsical broken world ruled by a dark apocalyptic cult. Search for loot, explore and survive. Build your own hideouts, protect and defend them to not get overrun by the eerie creatures that hunt you at nighttime.

name: Sky of Tides
description: Sky of Tides is a sci-fi narrative game set in a technologically advanced universe on the brink of war. Play as Rin, who must search for her missing father and heal the broken planet of Numen. Explore the world while your choices shape your character.

name: Last Protection
description: The barbarians are trying to enslave your kingdom, stop them!

name: Trapper Simulator
description: Be stealth be silent setup the perfect traps! Use your brain more than a weapon and show your skills, you need them to survive. Let's begin Hunting.

name: Nobunaga's Ambition: Taishi Deluxe Edition
description:
Deluxe Edition Contents
'NOBUNAGA'S AMBITION: Taishi' Game
NOBUNAGA'S AMBITION: Taishi: Season Pass
Scenario 'Fateful Clash'
Scenario 'Jiro-Hoshi Naotora'
Maiden CG Set: WomenRulers

name: Muramasa Rebirth Complete Collection
description:
Like the name says, 'Muramasa Rebirth: Complete Collection' brings together the original game and all four of the 'Genroku Legends' into one convenient package! Experience the stories of the possessed princess Momohime and the fugitive ninja Kisuke, as well as those of Okoi, the demon-cat out to avenge her owner the downtrodden farmer Gonbe, who has taken it upon himself to ask the powers that be to re-think the taxes that are driving his village to ruin Arashimaru, a world-weary ninja on the run from his former clan and cursed by a vengeful goddess and Rajyaki, the youngest daughter of the ruler of Hell, who is on a mission to find the treasures belonging to the Seven Gods of Fortune while trying to be the best fiancee she can be!
With beautiful, hand-drawn 2-D art, intense hack-and slash game play, and epics tales of betrayal, vengeance, hope, and redemption, 'Muramasa Rebirth: Complete Collection' is a must-have for the PlayStationVita handheld entertainment system!

name: The Crew 2: Steelbook Gold Edition
description:
Take on the American motorsports scene as you explore the USA in one of the most exhilarating open worlds ever created. With a wide variety of vehicles to choose from, experience the thrill and excitement of competing across the USA as you test your skills in a wide range of disciplines.

Get The Crew 2 three days early with the Gold Edition. It also features:
• SteelBook
• Season Pass
• The Crew 2 Motorsports Deluxe Pack, which includes:
• Ford F-150 Raptor Race Truck 2017
• Abarth 500 2008 Monster Truck Editions
• Pilatus PC-21
• Three outfits to customize your avatar

name: The Caligula Effect: Deluxe Digital Bundle
description:
The Caligula Effect: Deluxe Digital Bundle includes: 
 
Game 
Swimsuit DLC 
Original Vita theme 
19 Avatars

name: 4-Block Dungeon
description:
In this game, you create the dungeon and explore it at the same time! Control the falling pieces, move them, rotate them, connect them and make them fit together. As the knight, wander the maze-like structure looking for gold and defeating enemies.

Jut like in the classic puzzle game Tetris, creating a full row of tiles will make them disappear. And that includes whatever was inside them! So be careful not to place your knight inside a line that is being cleared!

The goal of this prototype version of the game is to collect as much loot and level up by defeating the enemies before the map gets filled to the top. When that happens, a portal will appear. Reaching it will mean victory.

Getting stuck with no way out is not uncommon inside a dungeon. Luckily for you, the knight is very resourceful and can use different tools to help him during the exploration:
- Hammers can create a tile of walkable ground in front of you
- Pickaxes let you break walls
- Bombs let you destroy tiles (this can be helpful to fit rooms together)

name: Door Knocker
description:
There's only one door. 
 
It's time to place door and kick door, and that's all I do.

name: Boxy Trial
description: In Boxy Trial you explore large levels in search for coins. Be clever. Use gravity changes, wall-jumping, and boats to your advantage. You need 50 coins to beat a level, but if you really feel like it, you'll want to maximize your coin-collecting game by getting all 99 coins in the level.

name: Poupée Girl DS 2: Elegant Mint Style
Beauty and Violence: Valkyries
description: A third-person fast-paced ARPG. Customize your female warriors and bring them to the most brutal combat. Slash your enemies into pieces, gut them, and release the darkest side of Valkyries.

name: MaguSphere: Magical Cannon Girls
description: Take on the role of a cute girl armed with a stupidly powerful "Magical Cannon" and destroy your enemies and the city in this Musou-style TPS game. Total destruction ("Full Break") of not only enemies but the surrounding city is key here. Get destroyin' and bring peace (?!) back to the city!

name: Jetpack Squad
description: A fast-paced shmup. Clearly, you're a cat, you've got a jetpack, and a big gun. In development since 2015.

name: Pro Strategy Football 2020
description: Incredible in-game editor! Edit teams, players, even uniforms! Multiple careers at the same time! Fully customizable rules! Complete game play by play! Improved playcalling!

name: Junk
description: Manage a community consisting of the craziest scum left on Earth after it was totally flooded. Expand your town, research craziest new technology, send expeditions to gather materials but whatever you do don’t let any of the groups living in your town gain more power than the others...

name: Birthdays the Beginning: Limited Edition
description: Limited Edition includes a World Guide, a Soundtrack, an "Avatar" Plush figure (approx. 7.25" tall), a Navi Charm, a Collector's Box and a Mystery Item.

name: Outcast: Second Contact - Digital Deluxe Edition
description: Make the most of the remake of this cult game with the Digital Deluxe Edition, which includes the Golden Weapons Pack and the Original Soundtrack.

name: Polyfuru feat. Asano Ruri
description: Enjoy the concert dancing with a virtual idol! This is a rhythm action game where you dance with glow sticks during VTuber’s performance. Enjoy the VR concert with Asano Ruri!

name: Auto Fire
description: Engage in classic car combat in a tactical RPG that roams across outlaw lands in a world where drivers are worshiped like celebrities. Salvage equipment and cars and build the sexiest, deadliest ride. Work for a corp, haul cargo, fight in the combat arena or become a savior. The choice is yours.

name: Angry Troll
description: Angry Troll is a Tower Defense game where you have to build attacking structures to fight off waves of evil trolls.

name: TinyWars
description: TinyWars is a "Storybook RPG" with tower defense style gameplay.

name: Balloon Fighter
description: Fly into the air and win balloon duels. You are hunting for wily chickens. Try to pierce their balloons, but do not let them break yours.

name: Rise of the Tomb Raider: Deluxe Edition
description: Deluxe Edition Includes Base Game and Season Pass

name: Sensible Blood Rugby Sevens
description: An hommage to classic arcade soccer games from the 90s , but adapted to the olympic sport of rugby sevens ! 1 or 2 players mode (up to 4 player modes expected soon), best enjoyed in local multiplayer. Try beating the referee and let’s put some blood on the field !!

name: Follow the White Rabbit VR
description: "Experience the world of colorful, tumbling down the rabbit hole with Alice" - Inspired by the 1865's classical English novel, 'Alice in Wonderland' , an ordinary high school girl from Korea takes a journey to a strange land with a white rabbit, in search for long lost key from her childhood.

name: Alien Monopoly
description: In different worlds, different groups of people compete for wealth and become the last strong.
